Webpage description (html):
All of our AWGifts-Dropshipping Wooden Incense Holders are imported from India. We deal with a number of companies all of which produce wood-wares in the city of Saharanpur in Northern India.

This area of India still faces significant infrastructure problems, electricity is intermittent, transport and roads are poor. As a result, supplies are particularly erratic. However the region has a proud artisan history of producing beautiful woodware and we are proud to support this industry by importing several containers a year of wholesale woodware, a favourite of which is the incense holder in so many forms.

Thank you for making us your Incense Holders supplier.

Great value, many designs to choose from. Order today.
